            "notes": "The deck revolves around utilizing land ramp and card advantage to quickly build up a strong board presence and overwhelm the opponent with aggressive creatures and efficient spells. By utilizing cards like Exploration, Burgeoning, and Azusa, Lost but Seeking, the deck aims to quickly advance its mana base and deploy threats ahead of the curve. Cards like Primeval Titan and Titania, Protector of Argoth provide powerful land-based synergies, while cards like Wrenn and Six and Nissa, Resurgent Animist generate card advantage and value over time. The deck can also utilize powerful utility lands like Dark Depths and Maze of Ith to control the board and protect its key threats."
